data.description: Built in 2019. This like new 4 BR 3 BA 2-story home with 2-car garage features a great room that connects to the dining and kitchen area. Also, on the main floor is a bedroom and full bath. The 2nd floor features the owner's suite with walk-in closet and private bathroom. Additionally, upstairs are 2 other bedrooms, another full bath, spacious loft, and the laundry room. Privacy fenced back yard. Large half acre lot. Great home for first timers, or downsizers. Make your appointment to tour it today.
